WEBVTT

00:01.520 --> 00:04.240
Just so you know, it was
Novak who lagged on you.

00:04.280 --> 00:05.880
[Reb]<i> Sheila's here.</i>

00:05.920 --> 00:07.520
Cops reckon she helped
Mendel poison everyone.

00:07.560 --> 00:08.960
She's been charged with murder.

00:09.000 --> 00:10.440
She used to drug some
of the girls with Rohypnol

00:10.480 --> 00:11.840
so Mendel could rape them.

00:11.880 --> 00:13.720
She is a fuckin' monster.

00:14.160 --> 00:16.200
Why does she hate me so much?

00:16.240 --> 00:19.120
If you testify on Friday
that her amnesia is genuine,

00:19.160 --> 00:21.640
she is going to use that
as the basis for her defense

00:21.680 --> 00:22.720
when it goes to trial.

00:22.760 --> 00:24.360
You know that, don't you?

00:24.400 --> 00:26.120
She will win that jury over
and when she does,

00:26.160 --> 00:28.120
they will drop the charges
for Bea's murder.

00:28.160 --> 00:30.840
I need your help to expose
Ferguson to Doctor Miller.

00:30.880 --> 00:32.200
[Reb]<i> I'll help you.</i>

00:32.240 --> 00:33.480
I'll tell the police
I saw Mendel

00:33.520 --> 00:35.040
make everyone drink the poison.

00:35.080 --> 00:37.080
You don't ever tell anyone
about what he did to me.

00:37.120 --> 00:39.760
If you think that Reb
is gonna bail you out,

00:39.800 --> 00:41.760
you're even fuckin' crazier
than I remember.

00:41.800 --> 00:44.040
Have you told Reb the truth
about you?

00:44.080 --> 00:45.800
No!

00:45.840 --> 00:47.520
I killed her. I killed her.

00:47.560 --> 00:48.640
Kath?

00:49.520 --> 00:51.960
There was no need for you
to assault the prisoner.

00:52.000 --> 00:53.680
You're suspended.

00:53.720 --> 00:56.120
So you heard what she screamed
in the corridor: "I killed her."

00:56.160 --> 00:58.120
Her blood has high levels
of LSD.

00:58.160 --> 01:00.120
Look, whatever she said or did

01:00.160 --> 01:02.240
under its influence,
it's meaningless.

01:02.280 --> 01:04.280
Reynolds told me it
was Novak who lagged.

01:04.320 --> 01:06.160
We're gonna take the bitch down.

01:06.400 --> 01:09.160
♪♪

01:36.480 --> 01:39.960
[baby crying]

02:05.640 --> 02:09.080
Why aren't you sleeping?
Alright, come on.

02:09.120 --> 02:11.800
Oh, it's alright. Here.
There we go. There we go.

02:12.240 --> 02:13.640
Oh, please, shh, shh, shh, shh.
Shh, shh, shh.

02:13.680 --> 02:14.920
It's alright.

02:14.960 --> 02:16.200
Shh, shh, shh.

02:18.400 --> 02:19.480
[gasps]

02:19.520 --> 02:20.720
[Greg] Sorry, Kath.

02:22.800 --> 02:25.440
I was just checking in to see
how you're feeling this morning.

02:25.480 --> 02:27.200
Any more hallucinations?

02:28.520 --> 02:29.680
No.

02:30.160 --> 02:31.240
Good.

02:32.160 --> 02:35.440
In that case, I'm happy for you
to return to your unit, okay?

02:37.560 --> 02:38.920
I don't wanna be alone.

02:42.400 --> 02:43.880
Please don't abandon me.

02:46.360 --> 02:48.880
[baby crying]

02:52.160 --> 02:54.160
[sighs]

02:55.600 --> 02:58.600
[indistinct chatter
and PA announcements]

03:02.000 --> 03:03.480
I know you lagged on me.

03:04.760 --> 03:06.720
You told the screws
I bashed the GM.

03:07.400 --> 03:08.640
You're delusional.

03:08.680 --> 03:10.600
I might see
what the women think.

03:11.840 --> 03:13.040
Knock yourself out.

03:15.520 --> 03:18.120
Tell me, Booms. You ready
to see your man, Gavin?

03:18.640 --> 03:20.360
No, I'm not ready to be dumped.

03:20.400 --> 03:21.960
No, that won't happen.

03:22.000 --> 03:24.280
He'll be onto you like
a seagull on chips, I reckon.

03:24.320 --> 03:26.160
Especially after I doll you up.

03:28.640 --> 03:30.080
Excuse me. Hey.

03:31.120 --> 03:33.760
-You agreed to help me.
-I'm not talking to you.

03:33.800 --> 03:36.040
Listen, whatever Lou
told you about me,

03:36.080 --> 03:37.320
I had nothing to do with--

03:37.360 --> 03:38.720
[Lou] Oi!

03:39.920 --> 03:41.760
Back the fuck off, Sheila.

04:05.040 --> 04:07.800
-So what's your story?
-It's not that interesting.

04:07.840 --> 04:09.800
Accused of poisoning
nine people.

04:10.880 --> 04:12.480
I'd say that's very interesting.

04:14.200 --> 04:15.480
Reb told me.

04:15.520 --> 04:18.480
But hey, relax.
I won't tell anyone.

04:18.520 --> 04:19.760
I'm innocent.

04:19.800 --> 04:22.240
I'm not here to judge.
Far be it from me.

04:24.800 --> 04:28.000
The doctor I was working for,
he orchestrated a mass suicide.

04:28.040 --> 04:30.480
Set fire to our retreat
and poisoned himself.

04:30.520 --> 04:32.760
Nothing to do with me.
I wasn't even there.

04:33.120 --> 04:34.280
Did you know
what he was planning?

04:34.320 --> 04:35.560
I had no idea.

04:35.600 --> 04:37.840
Then how did you know
it was him?

04:39.560 --> 04:41.320
He thought he was the messiah.

04:43.440 --> 04:46.360
You know, I've often wondered
why he left me behind.

04:48.200 --> 04:51.440
-And you believed in him?
-I was under his spell, yeah.

04:53.920 --> 04:55.440
But once he was gone...

04:56.520 --> 04:58.520
You cleaned out
the bank accounts.

05:01.240 --> 05:03.160
Reb must trust you.

05:03.920 --> 05:05.080
He does.

05:06.840 --> 05:08.560
He reminds me of my son,
actually.

05:09.000 --> 05:12.160
I didn't poison anyone,
and Reb knows it.

05:12.200 --> 05:13.360
Yeah, sure.

05:14.120 --> 05:16.200
But it's Lou who's the obstacle.

05:17.040 --> 05:20.240
She has way too much
influence over Reb.

05:21.600 --> 05:22.840
You know, I have to agree.

05:22.880 --> 05:25.640
♪♪

05:29.920 --> 05:31.200
Vera.

05:31.960 --> 05:33.200
You're late.

05:33.240 --> 05:34.560
Is everything okay with Grace?

05:34.600 --> 05:36.280
[sighs] Yeah, I've been up
half the night.

05:36.320 --> 05:37.840
I couldn't settle her.

05:38.120 --> 05:39.520
-Did you try walking her?
-Yes.

05:39.560 --> 05:40.840
-Burping her?
-Yes.

05:40.880 --> 05:42.800
-Swaddling her?
-Yes, Jake.

05:42.840 --> 05:44.600
I think she's picking up
on my anxiety

05:44.640 --> 05:46.520
about Ferguson's
committal hearing tomorrow.

05:46.560 --> 05:48.280
Hey, listen.

05:48.320 --> 05:50.680
Your little stunt yesterday
nearly brought us all unstuck.

05:51.240 --> 05:52.960
I seem to be the only one
who is worried

05:53.000 --> 05:55.040
about what Miller's
going to say.

05:55.840 --> 05:58.240
Yeah, she's probably got colic.

05:59.640 --> 06:00.840
I googled it.

06:03.560 --> 06:07.000
[indistinct arguing]

06:40.360 --> 06:41.960
[woman on PA]
<i>Attention all staff,</i>

06:42.000 --> 06:43.240
<i>visiting hours commence</i>
<i>in 15 minutes.</i>

06:43.280 --> 06:45.200
[chuckles]

06:52.920 --> 06:53.960
Come in.

06:55.040 --> 06:57.960
-Governor, can I have a word?
-What are you doing here?

07:01.280 --> 07:04.040
I'd like to inform you
that I've had legal advice.

07:04.080 --> 07:07.280
If you don't reinstate me, I'll
sue the department for my PTSD.

07:07.320 --> 07:08.960
Your what?

07:09.000 --> 07:11.680
-Post traumatic stress dis--
-Yes, I know what it is.

07:11.720 --> 07:13.840
It's the first
I've heard of it.

07:13.880 --> 07:15.240
Remember the siege?

07:16.400 --> 07:17.600
[sighs]

07:20.120 --> 07:21.400
[Ann] So it's all in order?

07:21.440 --> 07:23.720
Can you find the figures
and show me, please?

07:27.800 --> 07:30.080
[indistinct chatter]

08:07.200 --> 08:08.360
Are you Gavin?

08:10.640 --> 08:11.720
Susan?

08:11.760 --> 08:14.880
[chuckles] What the...?

08:15.280 --> 08:18.560
You don't look nothing
like this photo.

08:18.600 --> 08:19.920
That's--that's not even you.

08:19.960 --> 08:21.960
Well, this is hardly
a true representation.

08:22.000 --> 08:23.520
You lying fuck!

08:26.760 --> 08:28.400
Come on!

08:30.640 --> 08:31.880
Fuck Allie.

08:31.920 --> 08:33.880
I'm gonna flood
this prison with gear.

08:33.920 --> 08:35.640
See how she likes that.

08:35.680 --> 08:38.080
Shit, that reminds me. Trav's
been hassling us for that money.

08:38.120 --> 08:39.640
Oh, give me the phone.

08:41.000 --> 08:42.800
Hey, Mullet,
I got a job for you.

08:42.840 --> 08:44.400
Spread the word
the top dog lagged.

08:44.440 --> 08:46.680
See if we can start ourselves
a little mutiny.

08:47.240 --> 08:50.120
♪♪

08:50.160 --> 08:52.080
Um, I don't know where it is.

08:52.640 --> 08:53.600
Well, it's gotta be
in there, Reb.

08:53.640 --> 08:55.000
Yeah, well, it's not.

08:55.040 --> 08:56.760
Well it can't just fuckin'
disappear, so think.

08:56.800 --> 08:59.200
I don't know. I hid it in
the mattress and now it's gone.

08:59.560 --> 09:02.320
Fuck! Fuck!

09:02.360 --> 09:03.760
I told you to look after it!

09:03.800 --> 09:06.320
I told you not to let it
out of your fucking sight!

09:06.360 --> 09:09.400
Hey, stop it! Now calm down.
What's going on?

09:09.440 --> 09:11.000
Did you take it?

09:11.040 --> 09:13.480
Is that why you've been
sucking up to him?

09:13.920 --> 09:15.680
I saw Kath
with the phone yesterday.

09:15.720 --> 09:17.920
-Kath?
-Yeah.

09:19.320 --> 09:21.560
Maybe she can tell you
where she put it.

09:25.000 --> 09:26.600
You stole my fuckin' phone.

09:26.640 --> 09:27.720
No.

09:28.400 --> 09:31.080
I admit I used a phone
to make a call, but--

09:31.120 --> 09:32.360
Oh, you made a call?

09:32.400 --> 09:33.840
Well, you're supposed
to have amnesia,

09:33.880 --> 09:36.400
so who the fuck did
you call, Nut Busters?

09:36.440 --> 09:37.960
I don't know.
I was so confused.

09:38.000 --> 09:39.760
But I put it back
exactly where I found--

09:39.800 --> 09:41.400
Confused my arse.

09:41.440 --> 09:44.000
Give me the fuckin' phone
or I will tear this cell apart.

09:44.560 --> 09:49.080
No, no. Please. Please, please,
please, do not do this!

09:49.120 --> 09:50.560
I do not have your phone!

09:50.600 --> 09:51.840
Please.

09:54.400 --> 09:56.520
-Please--[screams]
-Fuck off!

09:57.560 --> 09:59.480
No, please!

10:00.880 --> 10:02.600
What do we have here?

10:02.640 --> 10:03.640
It's Wanda!

10:03.960 --> 10:05.920
Please be very careful
with that.

10:05.960 --> 10:07.480
They don't like to be jostled.

10:07.520 --> 10:09.600
Oh, honey,
I'm not gonna jostle her.

10:09.640 --> 10:11.960
I'm gonna make you
swallow the little fucker!

10:12.000 --> 10:14.480
No! No!

10:15.520 --> 10:17.680
-Hey!
-Give it to me, please!

10:17.720 --> 10:19.280
Give it to me! Give it to me!

10:23.280 --> 10:29.160
[screaming] No! No. [sobbing]

10:41.640 --> 10:42.880
No!

10:43.760 --> 10:44.960
No!

11:17.520 --> 11:19.280
<i>-I love you, Mummy.</i>
-I love you, Mummy.

11:21.240 --> 11:23.440
I love you, Mummy.

11:26.480 --> 11:28.400
I love you...

11:33.360 --> 11:34.880
I love you, Mummy.

11:35.640 --> 11:38.000
We can't put this down to LSD.

11:38.040 --> 11:40.120
Your tests are completely clear.

11:40.160 --> 11:42.440
It wasn't a hallucination.

11:46.440 --> 11:47.800
It was a memory.

11:48.720 --> 11:53.040
That child I told you about
wasn't someone I harmed.

11:53.760 --> 11:55.400
It was me.

11:59.800 --> 12:01.240
Are you sure?

12:02.280 --> 12:04.440
You're not simply
trying to rationalise--

12:04.480 --> 12:07.480
When I was a little girl,
my father murdered my mother.

12:10.000 --> 12:11.320
I was there.

12:11.520 --> 12:14.360
♪♪

12:14.400 --> 12:16.200
How did it happen?

12:19.440 --> 12:21.360
He drowned her in the bath.

12:22.200 --> 12:23.480
Did he go to prison?

12:24.480 --> 12:25.680
Don't know.

12:26.960 --> 12:28.360
This is a breakthrough.

12:29.080 --> 12:31.080
Kath, what else do you remember?

12:32.760 --> 12:33.920
Nothing.

12:36.680 --> 12:39.000
It's like a fragment
from a dream.

12:40.320 --> 12:42.040
Only I know it isn't a dream,

12:42.800 --> 12:47.000
because I feel it
in every fibre of my being.

12:51.160 --> 12:53.320
Linda just told me that
Ferguson had a freak-out.

12:53.360 --> 12:54.720
What happened?

12:54.760 --> 12:57.320
It wasn't a freak-out,
it was a breakthrough.

12:57.360 --> 12:58.720
She's remembered something.

12:59.240 --> 13:02.120
-What?
-A traumatic childhood memory.

13:02.160 --> 13:03.880
It's often a marker
in psychopathy.

13:03.920 --> 13:05.480
So that proves
she's been faking.

13:05.520 --> 13:07.160
Not necessarily, no.

13:07.200 --> 13:08.600
Well if she remembers that,

13:08.640 --> 13:10.320
she must remember
other things as well.

13:10.360 --> 13:11.920
Well, actually, a true amnesiac

13:11.960 --> 13:14.160
will typically
remember one or more

13:14.200 --> 13:16.640
usually painful memories
from early childhood,

13:16.680 --> 13:17.960
while more recent memories

13:18.000 --> 13:20.040
-remain inaccessible.
-Right.

13:20.080 --> 13:22.480
So you've made up your mind
about your testimony, then?

13:22.840 --> 13:24.040
[sighs]

13:24.080 --> 13:25.720
I'm sorry, Vera.

13:25.760 --> 13:28.400
I can only give the court
my honest professional opinion.

13:35.200 --> 13:37.040
If the DPP can't
get a conviction

13:37.080 --> 13:38.400
for the murder of Kath Maxwell,

13:38.440 --> 13:39.600
they will not pursue one
for Bea Smith

13:39.640 --> 13:40.760
and Ferguson will walk free.

13:40.800 --> 13:42.320
Look I know that, Vera,

13:42.360 --> 13:44.040
but there's no point in getting
all worked up about it--

13:44.080 --> 13:45.400
What, you think
she'll just stop there?

13:45.440 --> 13:46.640
She'll just take
a nice holiday?

13:46.680 --> 13:48.240
No, no,

13:48.280 --> 13:49.520
she will sue the department
for wrongful dismissal

13:49.560 --> 13:50.800
and take the Governorship back.

13:50.840 --> 13:52.000
Then she'll have
to fight me for it.

13:52.040 --> 13:53.360
You will be in prison!

13:53.400 --> 13:55.040
She will make sure
we all go to jail

13:55.080 --> 13:56.320
and Grace will end up
in foster care.

13:56.360 --> 13:58.040
You know, on some level,

13:58.080 --> 13:59.560
I think she knows that something
terrible's about to happen.

13:59.600 --> 14:01.520
-Ferguson?
-No, Grace!

14:02.120 --> 14:03.880
I couldn't stop her crying
last night.

14:03.920 --> 14:05.720
She knows her whole world
is about to come crashing down.

14:05.760 --> 14:07.000
Listen, you haven't slept
and you're stressed, okay?

14:07.040 --> 14:08.120
You're panicking.

14:08.160 --> 14:09.640
Yeah, for good reason.

14:09.680 --> 14:11.160
It's out of our hands.
There's nothing we can do.

14:11.200 --> 14:12.560
Yes, there is.

14:13.080 --> 14:14.240
Sack Miller.

14:16.160 --> 14:19.240
Oi, Trav, I need you to make
a payment for me to our friend.

14:19.280 --> 14:21.040
I can't access my account
right now.

14:22.560 --> 14:24.560
Yeah, I gave you
the log-in details.

14:24.600 --> 14:26.480
[woman on PA]
<i>Attention compound,</i>

14:26.520 --> 14:28.240
<i>all prisoners return</i>
<i>to their units immediately.</i>

14:28.280 --> 14:30.320
<i>Count will commence</i>
<i>in ten minutes.</i>

14:31.200 --> 14:34.440
What do you mean, there's no
available funds? There's heaps.

14:36.040 --> 14:37.680
No, that's fucking wrong.

14:39.320 --> 14:41.200
Well, what was
the last withdrawal?

14:42.600 --> 14:45.800
You call the bank, you get them
to trace that. That wasn't me.

14:46.240 --> 14:48.040
It wasn't fucking me!

14:48.080 --> 14:50.320
Fuck! Fuck!

14:50.360 --> 14:51.840
Fuck!

14:51.880 --> 14:55.200
But not only is he,
like, a friggin' liar,

14:55.240 --> 14:56.960
he's also the ugliest
motherfucker

14:57.000 --> 14:58.280
I've ever laid eyes on.

14:58.600 --> 15:00.080
-Really?
-Yes.

15:00.400 --> 15:02.560
Well, you weren't exactly
up front with Gavin

15:02.600 --> 15:03.760
about yourself, either.

15:04.200 --> 15:06.680
No, you know, you,
you told me to tell him

15:06.720 --> 15:08.320
that I was a swimwear model

15:08.360 --> 15:10.560
and that I liked to suck on big
spoons like Nigella.

15:10.600 --> 15:12.640
-No.
-That was you.

15:12.680 --> 15:14.960
No, you were the one that was
like, "Oh, I look like Allie."

15:15.000 --> 15:17.880
Look, obviously he's insecure
about himself too.

15:17.920 --> 15:19.400
I'm not insecure.

15:19.440 --> 15:20.880
Look, all I'm saying is,

15:20.920 --> 15:23.360
maybe you can take
a less superficial approach.

15:23.400 --> 15:25.360
[sighs] I don't even know
what that means.

15:26.000 --> 15:27.600
It's what's on the inside
that counts.

15:28.440 --> 15:30.640
Plus, I didn't write
all those letters for nothin'.

15:30.680 --> 15:32.200
For fuck's sake,

15:32.240 --> 15:33.880
do we really have to listen
to this inane drivel?

15:34.320 --> 15:37.320
Shut up! We had to listen
to your acid trip.

15:37.360 --> 15:41.120
Oh, no, I'm not going back!
I'm not going back!

15:41.160 --> 15:43.120
Stop looking at me
with your eyes!

15:43.160 --> 15:44.360
Boomer.

15:46.880 --> 15:48.040
Hey.

15:48.560 --> 15:50.240
You okay?

15:50.280 --> 15:52.880
Guess I'll have plenty
of peace and quiet in Gitmo.

15:53.360 --> 15:54.920
I wish there was something
we could do.

15:54.960 --> 15:56.000
Thanks.

15:56.720 --> 16:00.480
Hey, you should know, Lou's
spreading the word you lagged.

16:00.720 --> 16:01.800
Fuck.

16:02.240 --> 16:03.560
How did she find out?

16:08.360 --> 16:09.960
So fucking close.

16:10.000 --> 16:11.800
I had the money.
I had the approval.

16:11.840 --> 16:13.560
I wasn't gonna have
to live like this.

16:13.600 --> 16:15.200
I will find out
who took the phone.

16:15.240 --> 16:17.240
I will make them pay the money
back, or I'll kill them.

16:17.280 --> 16:19.640
Then I'll never
get my surgery, so...

16:20.600 --> 16:21.760
Okay.

16:23.280 --> 16:25.600
So it's gone missing
while I was in the slot.

16:26.440 --> 16:29.000
What if Novak lagged
to put me in there

16:29.040 --> 16:30.480
so she could
steal the money?

16:30.520 --> 16:32.440
But how could she get
into our account?

16:32.480 --> 16:34.240
Fuck knows
she could have found a way.

16:34.280 --> 16:36.840
She's threatened to put us
out of business before.

16:36.880 --> 16:38.160
It makes sense.

16:39.320 --> 16:41.480
-Shit.
-What?

16:42.000 --> 16:44.480
I saw her coming out
of our unit yesterday.

16:44.520 --> 16:47.400
♪♪

17:00.480 --> 17:01.680
Hi.

17:05.160 --> 17:08.320
Hi. Thanks for coming in.

17:08.800 --> 17:11.240
I'm sorry about yesterday.

17:11.280 --> 17:13.320
I'm really glad you called.

17:13.360 --> 17:15.240
And I'm sorry
about my photograph.

17:15.280 --> 17:18.840
I was just worried that I might
not be good enough for you.

17:19.360 --> 17:22.160
I guess we've both been
guilty of a little subterfuge.

17:22.200 --> 17:23.240
And lying.

17:23.280 --> 17:24.880
[laughs]

17:24.920 --> 17:26.440
[laughs]

17:26.480 --> 17:28.720
I really love your sense
of humour, Susan.

17:28.760 --> 17:31.360
It's one of the first things
that attracted me to you.

17:31.400 --> 17:33.640
-Yeah?
-That and your writing.

17:34.560 --> 17:37.560
Your letters really
turned me on.

17:39.080 --> 17:40.440
Right.

17:40.480 --> 17:41.800
[laughs]

17:41.840 --> 17:44.120
Well, you know
you're no slouch yourself.

17:44.160 --> 17:46.280
-No.
-Yeah, serious.

17:46.320 --> 17:48.400
That bit about rooting donuts.

17:48.440 --> 17:50.320
[both laugh]

17:50.360 --> 17:51.800
-That was funny.
-Silly.

17:51.840 --> 17:53.200
And sexy.

17:54.600 --> 17:56.720
Yeah, that's when I knew
you were special.

17:56.760 --> 17:58.520
Thank you.

17:58.560 --> 18:00.400
No worries.

18:00.440 --> 18:02.920
Have you ever thought
about doing it professionally?

18:02.960 --> 18:05.800
-Rooting donuts?
-No, writing.

18:05.840 --> 18:08.480
-Are you kidding me?
-No.

18:08.520 --> 18:10.000
I've been thinking.

18:10.040 --> 18:11.880
Well, I run an exclusive

18:11.920 --> 18:15.160
subscription-only website
called Slammer.

18:15.200 --> 18:16.840
Yeah?

18:16.880 --> 18:19.200
It's devoted to adult content
for prison fantasists.

18:21.400 --> 18:22.440
Jeez.

18:22.480 --> 18:25.000
What are the frigging chances?

18:25.040 --> 18:27.000
Of us. What are the chances?

18:27.040 --> 18:28.240
No, not really chances.

18:28.280 --> 18:29.920
You see, when I read
that Wentworth

18:29.960 --> 18:32.080
had jagged that
market research contract,

18:32.400 --> 18:35.120
I put my name down
on the call register.

18:35.160 --> 18:36.920
Hey, hang on.

18:38.080 --> 18:40.720
So you knew I was a prisoner,
like, all along?

18:40.760 --> 18:42.040
Yeah.

18:42.080 --> 18:43.600
See, I was hoping
to hook up with someone,

18:43.640 --> 18:45.880
someone just like you,
who could feed me

18:45.920 --> 18:48.600
some really knockout
inside oil, yeah?

18:49.760 --> 18:50.920
Yeah.

18:52.720 --> 18:54.920
♪♪

18:54.960 --> 18:57.040
I wanna know what the women
are saying.

18:57.080 --> 18:58.120
Go find out.

18:58.160 --> 18:59.280
Onto it.

18:59.920 --> 19:02.400
Hey, hot stuff, how'd it go?

19:02.440 --> 19:04.320
Oh. Gavin's a creep.

19:04.360 --> 19:05.760
What?

19:05.800 --> 19:07.080
I thought you were
giving him another chance.

19:07.120 --> 19:09.120
The bastard, like, catfished me.

19:09.520 --> 19:12.040
Yeah, so he by purpose got
on the call centre list

19:12.080 --> 19:14.200
just so he could find
a prisoner to,

19:14.240 --> 19:16.640
like, write sleazy shit
for his website.

19:16.680 --> 19:18.560
-You're not doin' that.
-No.

19:18.600 --> 19:19.720
You are.

19:19.760 --> 19:21.040
Wait, what?

19:21.080 --> 19:22.880
Yeah, I got a plan
and you gotta help me.

19:22.920 --> 19:24.720
No, no, no, I'm not writing
anything for his website.

19:24.760 --> 19:27.800
Please, 'cause Gavin
don't know it yet,

19:28.200 --> 19:29.880
but he's gonna pay
for your prison porn

19:29.920 --> 19:30.960
by being my spoof donor.

19:31.000 --> 19:32.360
Her what?

19:32.400 --> 19:33.480
My spoof donor.

19:34.040 --> 19:35.480
You don't even wanna know.

19:35.520 --> 19:37.640
Gotta go, guys.
I'll see you later.

19:38.480 --> 19:39.640
Ms. Bennett.

19:41.560 --> 19:43.360
What's happening with Ferguson?

19:43.400 --> 19:45.040
Did Doctor Miller
change his mind?

19:45.800 --> 19:47.360
On the contrary.

19:47.720 --> 19:50.000
He has been completely
sucked in by her.

19:50.040 --> 19:51.640
How? She confessed.

19:51.680 --> 19:53.960
He is putting that down
to the LSD in her system.

19:54.000 --> 19:57.440
If anything, he is even more
convinced that she is genuine.

19:57.480 --> 19:59.080
Can't you get him
to change his mind?

19:59.120 --> 20:00.640
I have tried, Novak.

20:01.400 --> 20:03.240
Believe me, I have tried.

20:03.280 --> 20:04.440
What, so that's it?

20:19.120 --> 20:20.320
[door opens]

20:22.200 --> 20:24.000
-What do you want?
-Our money back.

20:24.040 --> 20:25.320
What money?

20:25.360 --> 20:26.440
The money for my fuckin' surgery

20:26.480 --> 20:27.560
you stole
when you took our phone.

20:27.600 --> 20:29.440
I didn't take your phone.

20:29.480 --> 20:31.240
Oh. Well, then why'd I see you
coming out of our unit
yesterday,

20:31.280 --> 20:32.680
right before the phone
went missing?

20:33.800 --> 20:35.320
It wasn't me.

20:35.360 --> 20:37.960
Bullshit. That's why you lagged
and had me slotted.

20:40.440 --> 20:42.560
Hey, fuck off.

20:42.880 --> 20:44.520
Consider who you're talking to--

20:44.560 --> 20:47.160
[grunts] [gasps]

20:47.200 --> 20:49.080
I want it back. Now.

20:49.120 --> 20:51.400
Reb, don't stay.
Don't get involved.

20:51.440 --> 20:54.360
I am so sick of you
telling Reb what to do.

20:54.400 --> 20:57.520
Fuck off and keep watch
outside the unit.

20:59.800 --> 21:01.360
[Allie] I don't have it.

21:02.240 --> 21:03.840
-I didn't take it.
-Fuck you!

21:03.880 --> 21:05.400
[grunts]

21:08.840 --> 21:11.120
-Give me the fuckin' phone.
-No!

21:13.040 --> 21:14.360
I want it back.

21:14.400 --> 21:16.040
-[blow landing]
-[Allie groans]

21:16.080 --> 21:17.360
[coughs]

21:17.760 --> 21:19.480
[groans]

21:23.720 --> 21:24.920
Don't.

21:26.000 --> 21:27.160
Last chance.

21:33.440 --> 21:36.480
[alarm blaring]

21:36.520 --> 21:37.720
Fuck!

21:40.520 --> 21:43.280
You've got till dinnertime
to give me my money back.

21:43.800 --> 21:45.320
Or you're a dead woman.

21:48.680 --> 21:50.200
[woman on PA]
<i>This is a Code Purple.</i>

21:50.240 --> 21:52.520
<i>Officers required</i>
<i>in H1 unit immediately.</i>

22:00.240 --> 22:02.760
[panting]

22:23.920 --> 22:26.320
It's okay, Allie.
They've gone, sweetheart.

22:37.400 --> 22:39.680
-Whose side are you on?
-Reb's.

22:40.560 --> 22:43.360
'Cause if you kill Allie,
he'll never get what he wants.

22:44.200 --> 22:46.960
Bullshit. You're just trying
to protect an old root.

22:47.000 --> 22:49.040
Oh, you carry on about
everything you do for Reb,

22:49.080 --> 22:51.200
but maybe you don't really
want him to fully transition.

22:51.240 --> 22:54.400
'Cause you're doing everything
you can to sabotage it.

22:55.080 --> 22:58.840
You fucking bitch!
I will fuckin' kill you!

22:58.880 --> 23:01.160
Can't you see
what she's doing to you?

23:01.200 --> 23:04.600
-Don't make the same mistake--
-Enough!

23:09.000 --> 23:12.080
You're not my mother
and I am not your fucking son.

23:14.560 --> 23:15.880
Come on, let's go, babe.

23:26.160 --> 23:28.800
Winter, Governor
wants to see you.

23:39.600 --> 23:40.760
Come in.

23:43.560 --> 23:44.600
I've got Winter.

23:45.000 --> 23:46.840
Are you waiting
for legal advice?

23:48.160 --> 23:51.000
Vera told me anything to do
with Winter goes through her.

23:51.560 --> 23:53.040
Just bring her in, Linda.

23:56.360 --> 23:57.720
Winter.

23:57.760 --> 23:59.200
[receptionist]
Governor Jackson's office.

24:00.480 --> 24:03.560
I'll have to get him to call
you back. He's in a meeting.

24:05.600 --> 24:06.760
Take a seat.

24:17.720 --> 24:19.800
Actually, take a break.
I'll take the calls.

24:20.560 --> 24:21.760
Off you go.

24:24.280 --> 24:25.840
That's bullshit.

24:25.880 --> 24:27.600
The attending officer said
you pushed the panic button,

24:27.640 --> 24:29.080
so I know you were there.

24:29.840 --> 24:34.360
I was there, yeah. I went to see
Allie and found her injured.

24:34.400 --> 24:36.040
Fuck's sake, Marie.

24:36.080 --> 24:38.520
Allie is in Medical and
I think Lou Kelly put her there.

24:38.560 --> 24:41.920
But if you refuse to confirm it,
I'll slot you for the bashing.

24:41.960 --> 24:45.160
-Will, please, just trust me--
-Governor to you.

24:46.360 --> 24:49.440
I fuckin' trusted you once with
everything and you played me.

24:50.560 --> 24:52.200
I will never trust you again.

24:54.120 --> 24:56.400
[Will on intercom]<i> Alright, get</i>
<i>Ms. Myles in here, please.</i>

25:02.760 --> 25:03.880
Winter.

25:03.920 --> 25:05.120
Will.

25:09.960 --> 25:11.800
[male guard on radio]
<i>Gatehouse to Sierra 3.</i>

25:11.840 --> 25:14.400
<i>Governor, the prisoner</i>
<i>transport vehicle has arrived.</i>

25:17.360 --> 25:21.080
♪♪

25:29.760 --> 25:31.120
How're you feeling, Kath?

25:32.080 --> 25:34.840
A little nervous.
Not sure what to expect.

25:34.880 --> 25:36.000
Yeah, that's okay.

25:36.640 --> 25:38.200
I'll see you in there, yeah?

25:55.520 --> 25:57.000
Greg!

25:59.720 --> 26:02.440
You know the only leg
her defense has to stand on

26:02.480 --> 26:05.520
is your testimony that she's
a genuine amnesiac. That's it.

26:05.560 --> 26:07.480
If they exploit that
at the trial

26:08.080 --> 26:11.480
and can elicit just enough
sympathy from the jury,

26:11.520 --> 26:13.400
she will walk free.

26:14.720 --> 26:19.080
After all the terrible, terrible
things that she has done.

26:20.560 --> 26:21.840
If you are wrong,

26:22.800 --> 26:24.280
if she is faking,

26:24.920 --> 26:28.240
you will be putting a psychopath
back on the street.

26:29.200 --> 26:32.440
I am begging you, Greg. Please--
Please listen to me.

26:32.800 --> 26:34.200
This isn't just
about Kath Maxwell.

26:34.240 --> 26:35.680
No one can help Kath.

26:36.000 --> 26:41.520
But you think about
all her victims, in the future,

26:41.560 --> 26:43.000
that she will torment,

26:43.760 --> 26:45.280
and she will torture,

26:46.160 --> 26:47.400
and she will kill.

26:49.640 --> 26:51.640
You'll have them
on your conscience.

26:52.960 --> 26:55.640
And I will have them on mine
if you don't stop her.

27:03.760 --> 27:05.360
[woman on TV]
<i>Tight security surrounds</i>

27:05.400 --> 27:07.120
<i>the Melbourne</i>
<i>Convention Centre,</i>

27:07.160 --> 27:09.760
<i>and the US Secretary of Defense,</i>
<i>Michael Schwartz,</i>

27:09.800 --> 27:11.880
<i>will be attending today's</i>
<i>AUSMIN meeting.</i>

27:11.920 --> 27:13.840
<i>The motorcade will</i>
<i>be accompanied by...</i>

27:13.880 --> 27:15.000
Are you okay?

27:15.040 --> 27:17.120
-What happened?
-Lou Kelly.

27:17.160 --> 27:18.400
What?

27:18.440 --> 27:20.200
Oh, man, should never
have left you alone.

27:20.240 --> 27:21.560
Turn that off.

27:21.600 --> 27:23.360
What she did to the GM
was bad enough,

27:23.400 --> 27:25.080
but she's taken
this shit too far.

27:25.120 --> 27:27.560
-What are you gonna do?
-What Bea and Kaz would've done.

27:27.600 --> 27:28.800
We're going to war.

27:28.840 --> 27:30.080
Get the crew together.
We're going.

27:30.120 --> 27:31.960
Oh, no, no, no, hang on,
um, Allie.

27:32.000 --> 27:33.400
There's something
we need to tell you.

27:33.440 --> 27:35.000
Lou didn't bash the GM.

27:35.040 --> 27:37.960
We did. Me and Boomer.
And Judy.

27:38.000 --> 27:39.280
By mistake.

27:39.320 --> 27:41.360
How do you bash someone
by mistake?

27:41.400 --> 27:43.800
It was meant to be a prank
to leverage Smiles,

27:43.840 --> 27:45.480
but then Reynolds showed up,

27:45.520 --> 27:47.920
-and it all went to shit.
-Why did you tell me it was Lou?

27:47.960 --> 27:49.320
Take the heat off us.

27:50.000 --> 27:51.240
It was my fault.

27:52.200 --> 27:53.320
Okay? Don't blame them.

27:54.000 --> 27:55.800
I suspected Lou
was lagging to the GM

27:55.840 --> 27:57.880
and lured her to the kitchen
to prove it.

27:57.920 --> 27:59.640
-You fuckin' what?
-What?

27:59.680 --> 28:02.400
-You knew it wasn't Linda?
-So why did you bash her?

28:02.440 --> 28:04.520
The bitch has been riding me
since I arrived.

28:04.560 --> 28:05.680
When she showed up,
I just lost it.

28:05.720 --> 28:07.160
Oh, fuck!

28:07.200 --> 28:09.080
Hey, at least this puts
the lagging stuff to bed.

28:09.120 --> 28:10.800
Lou Kelly is one herself.

28:10.840 --> 28:12.320
You should never have
involved these two in this.

28:12.360 --> 28:13.480
I know.

28:14.080 --> 28:15.280
I'm sorry, I didn't think.

28:16.280 --> 28:18.160
-No, Allie, wait--
-Leave me alone.

28:26.240 --> 28:29.320
Does either side seek
to call the expert witness?

28:29.360 --> 28:31.840
Yes, Your Honour.
We'd like to call Doctor Miller.

28:31.880 --> 28:34.880
♪♪

28:45.040 --> 28:47.520
I do solemnly and sincerely
declare and affirm

28:47.560 --> 28:50.640
the evidence I shall give will
be the truth, the whole truth

28:50.680 --> 28:52.000
and nothing but the truth.

28:52.040 --> 28:53.960
Your witness, Ms. Casey.

28:55.560 --> 28:57.120
Could you please state your name

28:57.160 --> 28:59.040
and qualifications
for the court.

28:59.080 --> 29:00.680
Yes, Gregory Richard Miller.

29:00.720 --> 29:03.120
I have both a medical degree
as well as

29:03.160 --> 29:05.360
a specialist fellowship
in forensic psychiatry.

29:05.400 --> 29:08.400
The document I have given you
is a copy of an affidavit,

29:08.440 --> 29:10.360
with a psychiatric report
attached,

29:10.400 --> 29:12.080
which you prepared
for this court.

29:12.120 --> 29:13.960
-Is this true?
-Yeah, that's correct.

29:14.000 --> 29:16.440
Can you confirm the said
document was written

29:16.480 --> 29:18.640
after analyzing the defendant,

29:18.680 --> 29:20.160
Joan Ferguson,

29:20.200 --> 29:21.880
and that it was true and correct

29:21.920 --> 29:23.800
at the time you swore
the affidavit?

29:23.840 --> 29:25.680
I can confirm that.

29:25.720 --> 29:28.880
Doctor Miller, you're aware
that in a police interview,

29:28.920 --> 29:33.280
the defendant has claimed
complete and total amnesia,

29:33.640 --> 29:36.720
incurred as the result
of severe head trauma,

29:36.760 --> 29:40.200
rendering her incapable
of answering the charges

29:40.240 --> 29:42.880
related to the murder
of Ms. Kath Maxwell.

29:42.920 --> 29:44.600
I'm aware of that, yes.

29:44.640 --> 29:46.840
Having had the opportunity
to analyze the defendant,

29:46.880 --> 29:50.560
could you please summarise for
the court your expert opinion

29:50.600 --> 29:54.920
on whether or not you concur
with the diagnosis of amnesia.

29:55.320 --> 29:57.680
Yeah, in my professional
opinion...

30:06.880 --> 30:09.080
I believe Ms. Ferguson

30:09.120 --> 30:12.120
is indeed suffering from
what we call a fugue state

30:12.160 --> 30:14.400
as a result
of severe brain injury,

30:14.440 --> 30:17.360
characterized by complete
retrograde amnesia.

30:18.440 --> 30:23.000
How can you be certain
that your diagnosis is accurate?

30:23.040 --> 30:25.800
Well, I can only give you
my expert opinion.

30:25.840 --> 30:29.640
And are you willing to stake
your professional career on it?

30:30.160 --> 30:31.200
I am, yes.

30:31.240 --> 30:35.080
♪♪

31:09.120 --> 31:11.320
I'm happy to see you
up and about.

31:11.680 --> 31:13.200
Thank you for helping me.

31:13.240 --> 31:14.680
No problem.

31:14.720 --> 31:16.680
You shouldn't be
wandering around alone

31:16.720 --> 31:18.200
after what happened.

31:18.800 --> 31:20.160
Where's your crew?

31:23.240 --> 31:24.760
You wanna take a seat?

31:25.440 --> 31:26.600
or are you wondering,

31:27.400 --> 31:29.680
worrying what the women
are going to think,

31:30.000 --> 31:31.440
hanging with the pariah?

31:42.680 --> 31:44.440
Tell me what's going on, Allie.

31:48.440 --> 31:50.160
I can't trust anyone anymore.

31:50.200 --> 31:51.400
Including me?

31:51.440 --> 31:52.680
Especially you.

31:56.600 --> 31:59.200
This is not just a threat.
She'll follow through.

32:00.000 --> 32:01.960
Lou is fucking barking mad.

32:02.720 --> 32:05.960
So if you know anything
about a missing phone--

32:06.000 --> 32:07.840
I don't. I didn't take it.

32:10.200 --> 32:14.320
All I can tell you is the last
person I saw with it was Kath.

32:14.360 --> 32:15.720
Ferguson?

32:16.640 --> 32:17.680
When was this?

32:17.720 --> 32:19.280
Just before her acid flip-out.

32:24.480 --> 32:25.520
Ms. Bennett.

32:26.280 --> 32:28.400
I left before it was over.
I don't know the outcome--

32:28.440 --> 32:30.640
I need to see that video footage
from H6. Urgently.

32:30.680 --> 32:32.280
Why?

32:32.320 --> 32:34.960
Because I need to prevent
an all-out war with Lou Kelly.

32:36.760 --> 32:39.680
About this time, someone
stole Lou Kelly's phone.

32:39.720 --> 32:41.200
-Her phone?
-Contraband.

32:41.240 --> 32:43.000
And they used it to steal
all of the money

32:43.040 --> 32:44.760
that they'd saved
for Reb's surgery.

32:44.800 --> 32:46.840
Lou thinks it was me. It wasn't.

32:46.880 --> 32:48.400
But Marie saw Ferguson with it

32:48.440 --> 32:50.360
right before this
footage was recorded.

32:50.400 --> 32:52.480
Ferguson called me
the other day.

32:53.560 --> 32:55.160
Why would she want
to steal a phone?

32:55.200 --> 32:57.800
She's got bigger problems
with her committal.

32:57.840 --> 32:59.000
My God.

33:14.160 --> 33:15.840
<i>You've called Greg Miller.</i>

33:15.880 --> 33:17.640
<i>I'm not around my phone</i>
<i>at the moment,</i>

33:17.680 --> 33:19.120
<i>but leave a message and</i>
<i>I'll get back to you. Thanks.</i>

33:19.160 --> 33:20.200
[answering machine beeps]

33:20.240 --> 33:21.880
Greg, it's Vera.

33:21.920 --> 33:23.920
Call me as soon as you get
this message. It is urgent.

33:23.960 --> 33:25.800
And keep your eyes on Ferguson.
I think she's trying to escape.

33:27.360 --> 33:28.560
I need to go.

33:31.320 --> 33:33.240
I couldn't get on to Miller
to warn him.

33:33.280 --> 33:36.400
Did you try the brawler
officers? I'll call them.

33:42.120 --> 33:43.400
This is Governor Jackson.

33:43.440 --> 33:45.480
Can you call me
when you get this message?

33:46.120 --> 33:48.480
Okay, that's strange.
Went straight to message bank.

33:48.520 --> 33:49.600
No, no, no, no, no.

33:49.640 --> 33:51.200
I'll call the courthouse direct.

33:51.520 --> 33:52.680
Okay.

33:56.840 --> 33:58.440
This is Governor Will Jackson

33:58.480 --> 34:00.200
from the Wentworth
Correctional Centre.

34:00.240 --> 34:02.800
We have a prisoner
attending court this afternoon,

34:02.840 --> 34:05.920
but I can't seem to get through
to any of my officers.

34:07.320 --> 34:08.560
Right, I understand.

34:08.880 --> 34:10.360
What was the outcome?

34:10.960 --> 34:12.040
Okay.

34:12.440 --> 34:14.440
Right, thanks for your help.

34:15.280 --> 34:18.280
The cellular network around the
courthouse has been shut down

34:18.320 --> 34:20.360
-as a security precaution--
-The AUSMIN meeting.

34:20.400 --> 34:21.800
Yeah.

34:21.840 --> 34:23.400
And Ferguson's been
committed for trial.

34:23.440 --> 34:25.800
Even more reason
for her to make a move now.

34:25.840 --> 34:28.200
The brawler left with her
two minutes ago.

34:33.320 --> 34:34.480
What do you want?

34:36.360 --> 34:38.080
I heard about
your missing money.

34:38.120 --> 34:39.840
I'm willing to pay
for your surgery

34:39.880 --> 34:42.120
on condition that you
give me that statement.

34:42.160 --> 34:44.080
I don't want your filthy
True Path money.

34:44.120 --> 34:45.440
Still letting Lou control you?

34:45.480 --> 34:46.760
This has nothing
to do with her, Sheila.

34:46.800 --> 34:48.120
I know what you did.

34:48.160 --> 34:49.560
Yeah, well I guess
that comes down

34:49.600 --> 34:51.520
to how bad
you want that surgery.

34:52.440 --> 34:56.160
You drugged me with Rohypnol and
held me down while he raped me.

34:56.200 --> 34:57.760
I would rather stay
in a woman's body

34:57.800 --> 34:59.240
than take your fuckin' money!

34:59.280 --> 35:01.960
I bet that Lou hasn't told you
the full story.

35:08.080 --> 35:09.480
Vera, please sit down.

35:09.520 --> 35:10.760
You're starting to wear out
the carpet.

35:10.800 --> 35:13.040
They should be back.
Call them again.

35:14.560 --> 35:16.400
There's been some sort of major
incident at the courthouse.

35:16.440 --> 35:18.360
-Oh, fuck.
-Call the police.

35:19.760 --> 35:21.080
What?

35:22.400 --> 35:24.800
[woman on PA]<i> Attention</i>
<i>compound, attention compound.</i>

35:24.840 --> 35:27.200
<i>H Block is now</i>
<i>called for dinner.</i>

35:34.040 --> 35:35.280
They wouldn't tell me anything

35:35.320 --> 35:36.560
about the nature
of the incident.

35:36.600 --> 35:37.760
Do they know
where the brawler is?

35:37.800 --> 35:38.800
No.

35:38.840 --> 35:40.040
Shit.

35:40.080 --> 35:41.560
Alright, Vera,
go home, get Grace.

35:41.600 --> 35:43.320
-We've gotta get out of here.
-Oh, Christ!

35:43.360 --> 35:44.880
-Will...
-[Will] Yes.

35:44.920 --> 35:46.880
Excuse me, Governor,
the brawler's arrived.

35:46.920 --> 35:49.720
♪♪

35:54.160 --> 35:55.480
Is Ferguson in there?

35:56.560 --> 35:58.680
-Do you have Ferguson?
-I presume so.

35:58.720 --> 35:59.920
What do you mean, presume so?

35:59.960 --> 36:01.280
Because of the
heightened security,

36:01.320 --> 36:03.280
we weren't allowed
in the courthouse.

36:03.320 --> 36:04.760
The court guys
loaded the prisoner.

36:04.800 --> 36:08.040
And you didn't check?
Open the doors.

36:47.480 --> 36:48.880
You fucking liar.

36:49.400 --> 36:50.840
You stole Lou and Reb's money

36:50.880 --> 36:52.920
and you let me
get bashed for it.

36:53.440 --> 36:54.520
I'm so sorry, Allie.

36:54.560 --> 36:56.280
I never thought
they'd blame you.

36:57.560 --> 36:59.400
-I'm giving this back.
-No, please.

36:59.440 --> 37:01.800
I need that money
to fight my extradition.

37:01.840 --> 37:03.440
My father won't help me.
He's abandoned me.

37:03.480 --> 37:05.600
-Pay it back.
-But nobody knows it was me.

37:05.640 --> 37:06.680
-You don't need--
-I know!

37:06.720 --> 37:08.440
Jesus fucking Christ!

37:08.480 --> 37:11.160
You all lied to me,
every single person I trusted.

37:11.200 --> 37:14.560
-You're top dog. You can just--
-Yeah, I'm top dog. So what?

37:14.600 --> 37:18.080
Do you know what top dog is?
It's a poisoned fucking chalice!

37:18.600 --> 37:20.440
You bust your guts
for these women,

37:20.480 --> 37:22.840
and where does it get you?
Fucking nowhere.

37:22.880 --> 37:24.360
It gets you fucking shivved.

37:24.400 --> 37:25.680
Like Bea.

37:25.720 --> 37:26.920
Like Kaz.

37:30.280 --> 37:32.080
Why'd I think
I'd be any different?

37:32.120 --> 37:35.000
I can't even trust
my closest fucking friends.

37:36.800 --> 37:39.600
Fuck, I'm sorry. Allie, I...

37:42.000 --> 37:44.240
I'll do it, okay?
I'll return the money.

37:44.880 --> 37:47.080
Give me the phone.
I'll do it right now.

37:48.200 --> 37:49.560
I'll fix this mess.

37:50.000 --> 37:51.920
I'll make it right. I'm sorry.

38:12.200 --> 38:13.360
Hey.

38:14.800 --> 38:16.880
You skipped dinner.
Everything okay?

38:17.320 --> 38:18.440
Is it true?

38:19.440 --> 38:20.600
That...

38:22.120 --> 38:24.680
That you watched me get raped
and you didn't do anything?

38:29.640 --> 38:31.360
Can you say something?

38:34.040 --> 38:36.520
Can you fuckin'
say something, Lou?

38:39.880 --> 38:41.240
We were all forced to...

38:42.200 --> 38:44.960
participate in the therapy
and I just...

38:47.600 --> 38:50.520
-I just didn't--
-"I--I--" What?

38:50.560 --> 38:51.960
I just--I...

38:55.080 --> 38:56.800
Why didn't you do something?

38:56.840 --> 39:02.000
Because I am a weak
fucking coward and I froze.

39:03.720 --> 39:06.560
I just... I just froze.

39:08.480 --> 39:10.680
Before you got there,
that man...

39:11.640 --> 39:12.800
I thought that

39:13.400 --> 39:17.120
he was my soul saviour,

39:17.160 --> 39:21.320
and he'd taken away
all of this anger

39:21.360 --> 39:23.600
and all of this hatred, and...

39:25.720 --> 39:27.680
he made me feel really safe.

39:27.720 --> 39:29.320
And then...

39:30.760 --> 39:33.440
when I saw him do that
to you, I just--I just--

39:33.480 --> 39:35.120
My heart was ripped
when I saw that--

39:35.160 --> 39:37.920
No, no, no. You lied
to me this whole time.

39:37.960 --> 39:39.480
-No, Reb, please.
-Get outta my cell.

39:39.520 --> 39:41.960
-Get the fuck out of my cell!
-Please, Reb!

39:42.000 --> 39:44.440
-No!
-I killed them all!

39:46.280 --> 39:47.600
I poisoned them.

39:47.640 --> 39:49.920
I burnt the place
to the fucking ground.

39:50.960 --> 39:52.320
I'd do anything for you.

39:53.640 --> 39:55.480
Fuck!

39:57.920 --> 39:59.960
Hey, please!

40:00.000 --> 40:01.400
Hey.

40:01.960 --> 40:04.040
Please, Reb,
it's always been for you.

40:04.720 --> 40:06.160
Everything's been for you.

40:06.800 --> 40:08.920
And I would do it again
if I had to.

40:15.200 --> 40:18.680
You saved me, and for what,
you know?

40:19.320 --> 40:21.960
I'm still trapped
in this fuckin' body.

40:22.960 --> 40:25.040
That's Novak's fault.

40:28.560 --> 40:30.400
She stole your money, Reb.

40:35.800 --> 40:37.280
She has to pay.

40:41.680 --> 40:42.840
Do it.

40:42.880 --> 40:45.880
♪♪

41:07.760 --> 41:09.960
Looks like she's won again.

41:10.000 --> 41:11.840
If she managed to fool a shrink,

41:11.880 --> 41:14.400
the jury will be
a piece of piss.

41:45.640 --> 41:48.480
[grunting]

43:03.480 --> 43:06.400
[woman on TV]<i> Just to hand,</i>
<i>some breaking news.</i>

43:06.440 --> 43:08.240
<i>Police have now confirmed</i>

43:08.280 --> 43:10.800
<i>that in an incident</i>
<i>in the city this afternoon,</i>

43:10.840 --> 43:13.760
<i>the US Secretary of Defense</i>
<i>Michael Schwartz</i>

43:13.800 --> 43:17.840
<i>has been shot and killed</i>
<i>as he left his motorcade.</i>

43:18.440 --> 43:21.960
<i>Witnesses report seeing a lone</i>
<i>gunman fleeing the scene</i>

43:22.280 --> 43:24.680
<i>and a massive search</i>
<i>is underway,</i>

43:24.720 --> 43:27.800
<i>but the suspect</i>
<i>has not yet been apprehended.</i>

43:36.400 --> 43:38.360
The balance
has been transferred.

43:39.040 --> 43:40.480
Thank you for your good job.

43:50.160 --> 43:52.320
It shits me
there's nothing we can do.

43:55.400 --> 43:56.840
Spitbag her.

43:59.280 --> 44:00.560
With pleasure.

44:07.640 --> 44:10.360
-Did you forget something?
-Yeah.

44:11.320 --> 44:12.400
This.

44:12.800 --> 44:14.720
[gasps] What are you doing?

44:16.080 --> 44:17.480
Stop it! Please!

44:17.520 --> 44:20.320
Why are you doing this?
Take it off me!

44:21.800 --> 44:22.960
Take it off!

44:24.040 --> 44:25.040
Get it off me!

44:25.080 --> 44:26.560
[gasping]

44:26.600 --> 44:27.720
Take it off me!

44:28.080 --> 44:29.240
Get it off me now!

44:30.560 --> 44:31.760
Help!

44:32.760 --> 44:33.920
Get it off!

44:35.600 --> 44:38.040
[woman on PA]<i> Attention</i>
<i>compound, this is a Code Black.</i>

44:38.360 --> 44:40.440
<i>All prisoners return</i>
<i>to their units.</i>

44:40.480 --> 44:41.520
No!

44:41.560 --> 44:43.800
[screaming] No!

44:43.840 --> 44:46.520
-Get it off me!
<i>-I repeat, this is a Code Black.</i>

44:47.160 --> 44:48.360
Help!

44:49.880 --> 44:51.040
Somebody!

44:51.840 --> 44:52.960
Somebody.

44:53.000 --> 44:54.920
Please, don't leave me
like this.

44:54.960 --> 44:56.640
[panting]

44:56.680 --> 44:58.040
Get it off me!

45:01.000 --> 45:02.480
Get it off me!

45:02.520 --> 45:04.240
[distorted whispering]
[Joan]<i> Joan Ferguson.</i>

45:07.320 --> 45:08.880
Get me out of here!

45:10.360 --> 45:13.160
[Joan's voice echoing]
<i>Say it.</i>

45:13.200 --> 45:16.640
[gasping]

45:17.160 --> 45:18.560
Get me out of here.

45:19.280 --> 45:20.640
Get me out of here!

45:21.240 --> 45:23.360
Help! Help!

45:25.000 --> 45:26.000
No!

45:26.040 --> 45:27.360
[screams]

45:27.400 --> 45:29.840
No!

45:29.880 --> 45:31.960
♪♪

45:39.320 --> 45:43.160
[screams]

45:43.200 --> 45:44.400
Shut the fuck up.

45:45.440 --> 45:48.840
[panting]

46:10.640 --> 46:13.640
♪♪

46:27.400 --> 46:29.800
I am Joan Ferguson.

46:35.880 --> 46:38.320
I am the Freak.
